item.title: Westend set to shed office development
item.author: THE SUNDAY TIMES
item.description:
DWS, the German owner of Westend retail park in Blanchardstown in west Dublin, is preparing to sell part of the scheme, writes Linda Daly.
The real estate fund will bring the office element of the development to the market in the coming weeks, The Sunday Times understands.
